Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths\Nof half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Winds of War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone on the sub-bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Coaly, you're a big boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't cry over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. This is Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where your father grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was a wonderful man\Nwho you can be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are mothers all like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you haven't seen\Nyour mother in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Bright is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reckless, Mr. Bright! Fly higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see that up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could skim closer to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But our pilot doesn't have\Nthe necessary skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Bison. The Trojan Horse\Nis attempting to cross the mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them advance any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you join the Magella Attacks\Non the ground, open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Garma.\N- What is it, Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think the Trojan Horse\Nis flying like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To hide from our radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're setting up an interference field using\Nthe terrain and Minovsky particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the effect of\Nthe Minovsky particles is magnified.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However powerful,\Nour guided weapons are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to ambush them in a place\Nwhere we have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we overwhelm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?\NThe Dopp formations are withdrawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the Great Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy will probably amass\Ntheir forces near Mid Lake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because that will be\Nthe most disadvantageous point for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fate will depend\Non the success of the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro, we're counting on you.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it doesn't matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant. They insist\Non having a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...\NWe want you to leave us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Leave you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're in a combat situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Anges, a town near here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...is my husband's home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Home town? Never thought I'd hear\Na word like that in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to bring up my son\Nwhere his father grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say such selfish things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bright?\N- Sir. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We suggest a ceasefire to the Zeons,\Nand let these people off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,About them wanting a ceasefire\Nso they can drop off refugees?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- However...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the enemy's thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...but this can buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be our chance to reinforce\Nour slow-moving ground forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will increase our chance of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems his privileged boyhood\Nhas spoiled him. He's too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why are you breaking it?\N- What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We're blowing a hole in it\Nto fool the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely win this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't win, it'll prove your incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back now. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\NI want to raise my son on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you can't understand my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never really lived on Earth, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here it comes.\N- Right on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Big John.\NI have a visual on the White Base transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything unusual?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the side of the craft was hit by a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's our escort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi!\N- Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.\NI'm just worried about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain, a child is waving at us.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A lake...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember such a large lake\Nin this area...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's this lake called?\N- I think it's just some bomb crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where should we land?\N- Well, that's Mid Lake over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some habitable structures.\NOkay, let's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Commence operation!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's finally falling apart, thanks to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bobsun, come in. This is Big John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like our attacks\Nhave had a delayed effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How unlucky for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have surveillance keep an eye on it.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- It troubles me.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of the rotors has stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just being paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's descending.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Make this look like an emergency landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this kind of mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we fooled them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,4 elderly, 2 women,\Nand 3 children. 9 in total...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, they weren't here.\N- Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd sneak aboard some soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're monitoring them closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd go to\Nthose houses we saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to go to St. Anges?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If St. Anges is gone...\Nthen we will be back to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are that mother and child going?\NThere's nothing in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot and crew have ejected and\Nare headed for the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Amuro. They fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. I'm taking a little detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried about that mother and child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Garma is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't understand the feelings\Nof family men like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're coming back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are they going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu, please hurry\Nand open up the container.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Amuro. You go hide in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When the operation begins,\Nyou'll be behind enemy lines and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Amuro! Where are you going?!\N- Don't use the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy patrol craft is following\Nthat mother and child. Aren't you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did it go well?\N- We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Kai.\NAre you confident about trying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've seen the terrain of the battlefield.\NWe can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Guncannon and Guntank,\Nprepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, darling! Save my Coaly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hm?\N- See something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a flash. Let's check it out.\NMissile safety, off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! He saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you hadn't found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Reduce throttle!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Big John has stopped transmitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the patrol craft.\NLet's begin our attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you reduce altitude a bit, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we go any lower,move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do the best you can, Mr. Kai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're firing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,l-It's so powerful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you! I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Giyal! See it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new mobile suit to the right,\Nbehind the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're attacking the Trojan Horse\Nwith our backs to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. The Blackjacks on the left flank\Nhave moved another 3 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma, move the Blackjacks\Nwith their backs to the lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...in front of the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I believe it's only a matter of time\Nuntil the Trojan Horse falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The transport that crashed at the lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...is hiding a mobile suit.\NThat's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We never checked\Nwhat was in that transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit from behind the left flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,l-impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going according to plan.\NAmuro's attacking from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. The White Base will\Nconcentrate all fire forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the Magella Attacks directly in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We'll be hitting our own!\NHold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder how the fightings going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows who'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who wins or loses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll mean that there will be\Nmany more widows like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fallen asleep, Coaly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm in the Gundam,\Nhow can I fight all of those Zakus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can do this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They got the last Zaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Commander! Please respond!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Magella Attacks are wiped out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retreat! Retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I possibly explain\Nthis devastating failure to my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have a chance to redeem yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... we commanders have a duty\Nto boost morale on the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We must return to our unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest tonight in the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. Grow up big and strong\Nand protect your mother, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Until a year ago, this was St. Anges.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be for the best\Nif you join the others by the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Anges...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Coaly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that mother and child\Nmade it to St. Anges?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma Zabi personally launches\Na vengeful attack on the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle-weary Amuro\Nreluctantly fights in the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and finally engages in an aerial battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them realize Char's intricate plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
